These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, tennis, weightlifting, baseball
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is tennis##2
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | baseball | tennis | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
House: craftsman, ranch-style, victorian, farmhouse
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
3. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| House   | ranch-style | craftsman | farmhouse | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: whist, poker, canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
2. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing canasta is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Game   | whist | mah-jongg | canasta | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
