.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, r&b, techno, folk
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | soul | folk | r&b |

