1. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
3. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Cigar   | davidoff | cain | fonseca | vegafina |

