1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Hobby   | gardening | filmmaking | hiking | collecting |

