.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, april, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
4. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Birthday   | april | july | august | november |

