2. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |    3     |    4     |
| Transport   | quad-bike | snowmobile | bus | van |

