.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, techno, punk, disco
1. the fan of techno is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
3. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
5. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | disco | techno | trance |

